headline: RTX's Collins Aerospace providing upgraded avionics for in-service Cessna Citation aircraft
summary: Collins Aerospace, an RTX (NYSE: RTX) business, has announced upcoming functionality upgrades to Collins' Pro Line 21™ integrated avionics systems installed on in-service Cessna Citation business jets. Cessna Citation business jets are designed and manufactured by Textron Aviation Inc., a Textron Inc. (NYSE: TXT) company.
